11
00:00:49,820 --> 00:00:51,580
You're Detective Suk, correct?

12
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:52,760
Yes.

13
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:55,680
As your new chief, I would like to say thanks

14
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:59,480
for the fine investigative work that you've done on this case to help bring it to light.

15
00:01:00,140 --> 00:01:01,440
You're very welcome, sir.

16
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:05,200
