20
00:01:16,660 --> 00:01:18,360
Yes, sir. I'll be on my way then.

21
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:20,720
Oh, uh, one more thing.

22
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:26,140
That tall man who emerged as a suspect in Inspector Xie Man's murder,

