107
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:10,820
Yeah?

108
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:16,700
Don't you want to find out the identity of this so-called monster?

109
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,120
Yes.

110
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,020
